race.description: Jgp We Stand With Tassie 5th Grade F
race.comment: ARMARTA (7) comes off a (19.53) win last time, scoring by 5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 366m at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. HARA'S PUMPKIN (8) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including three wins and two placings. Comes off a (19.66) win last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths in a Grade 5 over 366m at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. SPECIFICALLY (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 1.75 lengths (19.78) behind HARA'S PUMPKIN at this track. Expected to be in the finish again. TITANIUM BLUE (3) will have admirers again after placing in a quick run last time out.
